This charming 1925 original Craftsman-style constructed home/office with POOL includes over 3400sf of usable space, including 2241sf of home/office, 720sf of indoor work/storage, and 500+sf of covered outdoor workspace. It is situated on a generous .90-acre premier lot with 164’ of Orange Ave frontage and 252" deep for endless possibilities! **Zoned both Residential & Professional use, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a home / business / office with options for workshop/storage space and great visibility with Direct Corridor Access to Downtown Eustis on FL-44.
Highlights:

BEAUTIFUL 4 BR CRAFTSMAN STYLE POOL HOME WITH GARAGE AND WORKSHOP ON .90 ACRES. This charming 2,241 SF home is centrally located and perfect for your next residence and as an added bonus you have the option of working from home or to have a high exposure office / home-based business! This home is zoned RP (Residential / Professional) and has an Urban Medium Future Land Use Classification (FLUC) in accordance with the 2030 Comprehensive Plan. TYPICAL USES INCLUDE: Residential; Nursing and personal care facilities; Civic uses; Residential professional offices; Passive parks; Religious organization.  Lot could also be split, or an Accessory Dwelling Unit could be added.  Please do your own due diligence to verify zoning info.

Enjoy living less than 2 miles from historic downtown Eustis with quaint shops, restaurants, frequent hometown festivals and vibrant Ferran Park on Lake Eustis. Circa 1925 adorable bungalow with wonderful updates and cherished original touches. Gabled roof, wrap-around front porch with beadboard ceiling, wood-trimmed windows, long U shape driveway to the 2-car garage. Relax on the front porch, then step inside to a bright, open floor plan brimming with old-world character. Abundant wood-trimmed windows, gleaming original hardwood floors, gorgeous living room brick fireplace flanked with built-in bookcases and arched opening into a gracious, wood floor dining room. Tastefully updated kitchen with classic Shaker-style cabinetry painted crisp white and accented with subway tile backsplash. Granite counters with prep island, stainless appliances, closet pantry and dining nook. 3 spacious, tiled (in 2020 with sub floor) bedrooms with an attractive, updated full bathroom with dual sinks. Expansive family room provides plenty of room to entertain, especially with double doors opening to the large pool deck with fenced back yard and covered pavilion for outdoor parties and dining. There's also a bonus room / mud room adjacent to the family room, plus a 2-car garage with a full bathroom, workshop and covered carport!

You won’t want to miss this extraordinary property!
